title: Kuba Discography (320 kbps)
description:
Laurence Harvey, an ambient, dub and downtempo producer from Cambridge, UK.

His debut album Inside Out (2006) was released on liquid sound design (Dragonfly Records sister label). The other three productions: Through a Lense (2007), How The Future Sounded (2008) and Bringing It All Back Home (2009) were released by Chillcode music.


Albums:

Inside Out (2006)
Through A Lens (2007)
How The Future Sounded (2008)
Bringing It All Back Home (2009)
Random Precision (2012)
Labyrinth of Colours EP (2012)
